---
---

<div class="report-phone">
  <div class="report-phone__frame">
    <div class="report-phone__card">
      <div class="report-phone__header">
        <div>
          <p class="report-phone__eyebrow">Viewing report</p>
          <p class="report-phone__title">Kastanienallee 48</p>
        </div>
        <span class="report-phone__badge">Delivered</span>
      </div>

      <div class="report-phone__grid">
        <figure class="report-phone__photo report-phone__photo--wide">
          <img src="/report/living-room.png" alt="Living room with natural light during the viewing" />
        </figure>
        <figure class="report-phone__photo">
          <img src="/report/kitchen.png" alt="Kitchen photographed during the viewing" />
        </figure>
        <figure class="report-phone__photo">
          <img src="/report/bedroom.png" alt="Bedroom photographed during the viewing" />
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="report-phone__notes">
        <div class="report-phone__note">
          <span class="report-phone__note-icon report-phone__note-icon--sun" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path
                d="M8 1.5v1.2M8 13.3v1.2M3.1 3.1l.9.9M12 12l.9.9M1.5 8h1.2M13.3 8h1.2M3.1 12.9l.9-.9M12 4l.9-.9"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
              />
              <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="3.1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p>Bright in the afternoon - living room faces south-west, plenty of natural light.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="report-phone__note">
          <span class="report-phone__note-icon report-phone__note-icon--sound" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path
                d="M2 9.5V6.5h2.4L8 3.5v9L4.4 9.5H2Z"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.2"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              />
              <path
                d="M10.2 5.8c.8.7 1.3 1.7 1.3 2.7s-.5 2-1.3 2.7"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
              />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p>Quiet street. Faint traffic noise from the front, back rooms are calm.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="report-phone__note report-phone__note--summary">
          <span class="report-phone__note-icon report-phone__note-icon--check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path
                d="m3.6 8.2 2.2 2.2 6.6-6.6"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              />
              <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <p><strong>Overall:</strong> well kept, move-in ready. Worth applying for.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
